                        <interp inst="t18750712-name-221" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH CHAMBERS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a tailor in the employment of Mr. Cook, and work outdoor—the book produced is mine—it is the practice of the cutter to initial all the items—I get paid upon that—that book contains a correct account of all the sums I have received—I have received no other sums.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18750712-name-222" type="witnessName">
