                  </hi>. I am a tailoress in the service of Mr. Cook—I work at home—the book produced is my book—it contains all the items of my work—it is initialled by the cutter, and I get paid upon that—it contans a correct account of all I have received and no more.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18750712-name-223" type="witnessName">
