                  </hi>. I am a tailoress in the employment of Mr. Cook—I work outdoors—the book produced is my book—that is my writing—it contains the items of all the work I do—if I have made a mistake the cutter has corrected it, then I get paid upon that book—I have to get it initialled by the cutter—I received no more than appears in that book.</p>
