                  </hi>. I am a tailoress in the service of Mr. Cook—on the 12th of June I received 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—that is all that was due to me—I did not receive 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I have not Got a book, they have taken it from me.</p>
